Use this tool to download vedios from chinese video site, from any country.

===================================
Usage:

-Bookmarklet
 1 Compress GetUrl.js to one-line-code and save it as a bookmark on browser.
 2 Open youku, e.g: http://www.soku.com/search_video/q_helloworld
 3 Click the bookmarklet, a textarea with all video links will show 
   at left-top window, with format: Video_Name	-#-	url 
 4 Save above links to a file. e.g: inputUrlList

-Shell
 Usage: nohup ThisScriptName inputUrlList [password] > somelog &

===================================
Requirements:
 python 2.5+
 curl command

===================================
Notice:

-Tested site:
 * youku.com

-Bookmarklet & Tested Browser:
 * Chrome

-Shell & Tested device:
 * my book live (a perface NAS with jail-break apple tv 2)
 * mac OS X 10.8.3

